Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:57.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没有斯巴达战士被丢下\N{\rYUANWEN}There was no Spartan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:12:59.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他已经死了\N{\rYUANWEN}He was already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:01.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她评估了情况 做出了决定\N{\rYUANWEN}She evaluated the conditions and made a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:04.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,什么决定\N{\rYUANWEN}What decision is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:07.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,什么时候开始我们会做决定了 我们不做选择\N{\rYUANWEN}Since when do we decide anything? We don't choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:11.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你告诉我们该去哪里 该怎么想 该杀谁\N{\rYUANWEN}You told us where to go and what to think, who to kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:15.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们每次都照做 绝不多问\N{\rYUANWEN}and we did that every time, without question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:18.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你像士兵一样服从命令\N{\rYUANWEN}You followed orders like soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:21.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-像机器一样  -你不是机器\N{\rYUANWEN}Like machines. - You're not a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:24.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那么我是什么呢\N{\rYUANWEN}What am I, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.85,0:13:28.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不要说人类 因为真正的人有自己的生活\N{\rYUANWEN}Don't say human, because real people have lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.02,0:13:31.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有家人\N{\rYUANWEN}They have families.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.73,0:13:33.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-有各种可能的未来  -你很伤心\N{\rYUANWEN}Possibilities. - You're upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:36.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-我们都是  -看看她\N{\rYUANWEN}We all are. - Look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:40.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,看看她\N{\rYUANWEN}Look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:41.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-告诉我你看到了什么  -放手\N{\rYUANWEN}Tell me what you see. - Let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:44.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,告诉我你看到了什么\N{\rYUANWEN}Tell me what you see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.58,0:13:47.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那是个女人还是把武器\N{\rYUANWEN}Is that a woman or a weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:48.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那是一个人吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Is there a person in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:50.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还是只是你留在\N{\rYUANWEN}or is that just a piece of equipment
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:52.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,战场上的一件装备 扔了就扔了\N{\rYUANWEN}you leave on the battlefield, dump and forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:16.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们把我们丢在那里\N{\rYUANWEN}They left us down there
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:18.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,自生自灭\N{\rYUANWEN}to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:20.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rYUANWEN}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:27.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没有撤离计划 没有战甲\N{\rYUANWEN}No evac, no armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:30.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-海军情报局知道我们肯定会死  -我知道\N{\rYUANWEN}ONI knew we wouldn't make it. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:32.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,致远星上的其他队伍呢\N{\rYUANWEN}What about the other teams on Reach?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:34.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有动静吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Any contact?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:44.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一片混乱\N{\rYUANWEN}It was chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.39,0:14:46.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这座城市沦陷了\N{\rYUANWEN}The city fell.
