Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.65,0:14:58.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-多久了  -两天\N{\rYUANWEN}How long? - Two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:01.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-两天  -两天\N{\rYUANWEN}Two days. - Two days?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:03.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们得回去\N{\rYUANWEN}We gotta get back.
