Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.58,0:15:09.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,致远星的人们需要我\N{\rYUANWEN}People on Reach, they need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.79,0:15:12.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不 他们不需要\N{\rYUANWEN}No, they don't.
