Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:41.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我告诉艾克森了\N{\rYUANWEN}I told Ackerson.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:50.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们已经知道了\N{\rYUANWEN}They already knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:52.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们知道\N{\rYUANWEN}They knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:54.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们还是什么也没做\N{\rYUANWEN}And they did nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:15:57.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我本可以阻止这一切的\N{\rYUANWEN}I could have stopped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:03.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果我 有战甲的话\N{\rYUANWEN}If I just...had my armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:06.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果她和我在一起的话\N{\rYUANWEN}If she was with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.93,0:16:09.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,致远星沦陷不是意外\N{\rYUANWEN}Reach wasn't an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:12.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是计划内的\N{\rYUANWEN}It was a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:15.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们需要小心行事\N{\rYUANWEN}We need to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:17.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,藏起来\N{\rYUANWEN}Invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:19.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你明白吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Do you understand?
