Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.64,0:16:58.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,下次 你可以直接按那个小按钮\N{\rYUANWEN}Next time, you can just push the little button there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:02.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,真有意思\N{\rYUANWEN}Fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:06.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是艘星盟的飞船\N{\rYUANWEN}This is a Covenant ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:08.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是狂徒尊者\N{\rYUANWEN}This is the command vesse
