Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:23.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是科塔娜\N{\rYUANWEN}I am Cortana,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:26.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-最先进的人工智  -不\N{\rYUANWEN}the most advanced artificial- - - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.59,0:17:27.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你对他来说\N{\rYUANWEN}What are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:31.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是什么\N{\rYUANWEN}to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:33.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,士官长吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Master Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:35.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我\N{\rYUANWEN}I
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:38.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们一起工作\N{\rYUANWEN}We work together.
