Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:57.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,给我看看他对光环的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:17:59.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,它不属于你\N{\rYUANWEN}It doesn't belong to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.21,0:18:02.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我也不属于你
