Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.25,0:30:38.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你为什么这么大只啊\N{\rYUANWEN}Why'd you have to be so big?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.88,0:30:42.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,走啊\N{\rYUANWEN}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.22,0:30:45.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这样如何\N{\rYUANWEN}How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.27,0:30:54.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是 我也是\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.78,0:31:03.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,伤害不断累积\N{\rYUANWEN}Damage accumulates.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.91,0:31:08.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她回不去以前的状态了 但时间会帮到她\N{\rYUANWEN}She won't be the same as she was, but time will help.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.20,0:31:12.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,里兹会活下来 会再次投入战斗\N{\rYUANWEN}Riz will live and she will fight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.08,0:31:15.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们所有人都不复以往了\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, none of us are what we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.59,0:31:17.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在我们可有可无\N{\rYUANWEN}And now we're expendable.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.13,0:31:21.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,致远星上发生的事并不是针对个人\N{\rYUANWEN}What happened on Reach wasn't personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.76,0:31:24.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,甚至不是策略需要 是政治原因\N{\rYUANWEN}It wasn't even strategic. It was political.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.39,0:31:25.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是巴拉戈斯基\N{\rYUANWEN}It was Parangosky.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.81,0:31:30.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是\N{\rYUANWEN}This...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.81,0:31:33.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,事关控制权\N{\rYUANWEN}This was about control.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.60,0:31:37.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,事关由谁决定这场战争怎么打\N{\rYUANWEN}About who dictates how this war is fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.78,0:31:41.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她赢了\N{\rYUANWEN}She won.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.61,0:31:46.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你没法为整个星球哀悼\N{\rYUANWEN}You can't grieve an entire planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.95,0:31:49.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,太宏大了\N{\rYUANWEN}It's too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.45,0:31:51.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们的思想不会让它成为现实\N{\rYUANWEN}Our minds won't let it be real.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.50,0:31:56.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所有这此生命 这些名字\N{\rYUANWEN}AlI those lives. All those names.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.96,0:31:59.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,太多了\N{\rYUANWEN}It's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.84,0:32:03.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我要你帮我做件事\N{\rYUANWEN}I need you to do something for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.13,0:32:07.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我之前没机会埋葬别人\N{\rYUANWEN}I never got to bury anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.64,0:32:10.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没埋葬过我的人民\N{\rYUANWEN}Not my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.68,0:32:12.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我的家人\N{\rYUANWEN}Not my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.98,0:32:17.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不知怎么的 我需要你当所有逝者\N{\rYUANWEN}Somehow, I need you to be everyone that's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.19,0:32:21.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你能做到吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.20,0:32:29.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,取出科塔娜的人就是巴拉戈斯基\N{\rYUANWEN}Parangosky's the one who took Cortana out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.70,0:32:32.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你怎么可能记得这些\N{\rYUANWEN}How could you possibly have remembered that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.33,0:32:33.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不清楚\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.21,0:32:39.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,里面有个空间\N{\rYUANWEN}There's a space inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.17,0:32:41.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那里曾经有个声音\N{\rYUANWEN}where there used to be a voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.38,0:32:44.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我觉得有人认识我\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm feeling that somebody knew me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.88,0:32:48.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有些东西\N{\rYUANWEN}There was something that
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.64,0:32:51.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,科塔娜说\N{\rYUANWEN}Cortana said.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.39,0:32:54.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就在她\N{\rYUANWEN}right before she
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.73,0:32:56.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,继续\N{\rYUANWEN}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.98,0:32:59.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,什么 她说了什么\N{\rYUANWEN}What? What- - What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.15,0:33:04.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你是怎么选的\N{\rYUANWEN}How did you choose
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.82,0:33:06.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\rYUANWEN}W- W- W- What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.99,0:33:08.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你是怎么选上我的\N{\rYUANWEN}How did you choose me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.03,0:33:13.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们创建了基因档案\N{\rYUANWEN}We created the genetic profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.91,0:33:15.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-调查过所有孩子  -不是\N{\rYUANWEN}We surveyed all the children- - - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.17,0:33:20.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,为什么选我\N{\rYUANWEN}Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.71,0:33:27.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-我不明白  -你明白的\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't understand. Yes, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.05,0:33:31.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,说实话\N{\rYUANWEN}Tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.06,0:33:34.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就这一次\N{\rYUANWEN}Just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.61,0:33:49.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还没聊完呢\N{\rYUANWEN}We're not done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.95,0:33:56.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,后退\N{\rYUANWEN}Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.79,0:34:01.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,再靠近一步 我就拉你们陪葬了\N{\rYUANWEN}Come closer, I will dig another hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.13,0:34:02.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你干什么呢  -嘿\N{\rYUANWEN}What are you doing? - Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.71,0:34:04.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这帮疯子要带走他\N{\rYUANWEN}This crazy's trying to take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.63,0:34:06.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你不能把他埋入地下\N{\rYUANWEN}You can't put him in the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.76,0:34:08.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不同意\N{\rYUANWEN}I beg to differ!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.97,0:34:10.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,把这尸体烧了 让他去找自己的路\N{\rYUANWEN}Burn this body. Let him find his way.
