Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.08,0:34:36.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是失去\N{\rYUANWEN}This is loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.41,0:34:38.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是有区别的\N{\rYUANWEN}There's a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.97,0:34:50.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,火葬吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Put him in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.69,0:35:07.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rYUANWEN}AlI right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.00,0:35:22.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-索伦  -在\N{\rYUANWEN}Soren. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.70,0:36:04.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-什么事  -晚上好\N{\rYUANWEN}What do you want? Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.25,0:36:05.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你这叫非法闯入\N{\rYUANWEN}You're trespassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.67,0:36:07.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-容我解释  -我们是来找儿子的\N{\rYUANWEN}Allow me to explain. - We're here for our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.00,0:36:10.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-什么  -我们的儿子\N{\rYUANWEN}Your what? - Our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.34,0:36:11.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,凯斯勒\N{\rYUANWEN}Kessler.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.59,0:36:13.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很听话的小男孩\N{\rYUANWEN}Nice boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.09,0:36:15.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-差不多这么高  -他是我们的孩子\N{\rYUANWEN}Like, yay, high- - The kid is ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.26,0:36:16.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,鬼扯\N{\rYUANWEN}- The hell he is. -
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.84,0:36:18.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,冷静一点\N{\rYUANWEN}Now...let's calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.72,0:36:20.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,去别地儿冷静去\N{\rYUANWEN}You can calm down somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.93,0:36:22.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这个家很好 他喜欢这里\N{\rYUANWEN}This is a good home and he likes it here,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.73,0:36:25.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,要是我把他交给了两个陌生人 那我是真该死\N{\rYUANWEN}and I'll be damned if I'm giving him up to a couple of strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.60,0:36:27.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们不是陌生人 我们是他的父母\N{\rYUANWEN}We're not strangers. We're his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.94,0:36:30.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就算是真的 你们也不会是合格的父母\N{\rYUANWEN}Even if that were true, some parents you'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.53,0:36:33.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他来到这里时 饿得半死\N{\rYUANWEN}He was half starved when he got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.24,0:36:36.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,看上去还挨了不少揍\N{\rYUANWEN}Looked like he'd been slapped around a little too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.78,0:36:38.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你说什么  -对\N{\rYUANWEN}- What did you say? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.78,0:36:41.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想现在知道罪魁祸首是谁了\N{\rYUANWEN}I guess we know who's responsible for that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.79,0:36:43.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,草 凯斯勒\N{\rYUANWEN}Fuck you! Kesslerl
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.79,0:36:46.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,凯斯勒 快出来\N{\rYUANWEN}Kessler, come out here right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.42,0:36:48.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,凯斯勒\N{\rYUANWEN}Kessler!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.29,0:36:51.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他就在这里 她们带走了他\N{\rYUANWEN}They have him. They took him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.63,0:36:54.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没事的 不会有事的\N{\rYUANWEN}It's okay. It's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.09,0:36:57.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-冷静  -我们要怎么办\N{\rYUANWEN}Calm down. - What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.26,0:36:59.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我在呢 我能处理好\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm here. I can handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.14,0:37:02.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-不就是场谈判嘛  -这关系到我们的儿子啊\N{\rYUANWEN}It's a negotiation. - It's our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.64,0:37:05.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\rYUANWEN}Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.31,0:37:08.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我马上回来\N{\rYUANWEN}I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.29,0:37:28.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吧 你们看上去\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, you all seem...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.96,0:37:31.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,准备充足\N{\rYUANWEN}ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.34,0:37:34.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你永远不知道世界什么时候会崩塌\N{\rYUANWEN}You never know when the world's gonna fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.34,0:37:36.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,确实\N{\rYUANWEN}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.59,0:37:41.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这茶真不错\N{\rYUANWEN}This is some really good tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.68,0:37:44.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你让我们给你五分钟\N{\rYUANWEN}You said to give you five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.77,0:37:46.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,已经过了两分钟了\N{\rYUANWEN}We already gave you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.02,0:37:51.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我小时候生活的地方和这里很像\N{\rYUANWEN}I grew up in a place just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.48,0:37:53.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\rYUANWEN}What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.15,0:37:56.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,意思是 我知道勉强维生是什么感觉\N{\rYUANWEN}It means I know what it is to scratch out a life.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.36,0:38:00.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,大地产出的粮食总是达不到预期\N{\rYUANWEN}The ground never gives you what it promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.49,0:38:03.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,吃的食物永远不够\N{\rYUANWEN}There's never quite enough to go around.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.83,0:38:05.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们凑合能过\N{\rYUANWEN}We get by.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.66,0:38:10.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我能搞来东西\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm the kind of guy that can get things.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.63,0:38:14.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,能给予你们补偿的东西\N{\rYUANWEN}The kind of things that can compensate.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.17,0:38:20.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道多一双手意味着什么\N{\rYUANWEN}I know what an extra pair of hands can mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.07,0:38:39.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们的儿子不卖\N{\rYUANWEN}Our boy isn't for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.54,0:38:56.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,实话和你们说吧\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm gonna be honest with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.67,0:39:01.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这里和我长大的地方完全不一样\N{\rYUANWEN}This is nothing like where I grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.55,0:39:05.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我出生在地狱里\N{\rYUANWEN}I was born in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.51,0:39:09.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在拳打脚踢下长大\N{\rYUANWEN}Raised in violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.43,0:39:12.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没有家人 没有家\N{\rYUANWEN}Being without a family, without a home...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.44,0:39:16.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没有食物 没有人保护我\N{\rYUANWEN}without food, without protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.90,0:39:19.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,凯斯勒\N{\rYUANWEN}Kessler!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.28,0:39:25.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,宝贝\N{\rYUANWEN}Baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.45,0:39:27.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我发现 我能挺过这一切\N{\rYUANWEN}I realized I can survive all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.71,0:39:32.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但是孤独\N{\rYUANWEN}But the loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.75,0:39:37.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,要说什么能要我命\N{\rYUANWEN}If anything was gonna kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.80,0:39:41.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那就是孤独\N{\rYUANWEN}it would be that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.97,0:39:43.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,真的是我\N{\rYUANWEN}It's really me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.30,0:39:47.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在我当父亲了\N{\rYUANWEN}So now I'm a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.22,0:39:48.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我生活在恐惧里\N{\rYUANWEN}And I live in fear
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.14,0:39:51.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\rYUANWEN}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.60,0:39:56.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不过我的儿子\N{\rYUANWEN}that my boy
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.06,0:39:58.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,永远体会不到那种感觉\N{\rYUANWEN}will never know that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.45,0:40:04.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,永远体会不到缺少爱是什么感觉\N{\rYUANWEN}That absence of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.41,0:40:12.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,感恩是你们收留了他\N{\rYUANWEN}I am grateful that you're the ones that took him in,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.50,0:40:18.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,因为我知道 他迟早能在这里找到爱\N{\rYUANWEN}because I know in time, he'd find love here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.13,0:40:25.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但他是我的儿子\N{\rYUANWEN}But he's my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.44,0:40:43.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你从哪弄来的这个\N{\rYUANWEN}Where did you get this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.36,0:40:46.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一个男孩给我的\N{\rYUANWEN}A boy gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.20,0:40:48.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在运输飞船上\N{\rYUANWEN}On the transport.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.70,0:40:51.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,用来保护自己的\N{\rYUANWEN}For protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.04,0:40:55.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他 他发现我害怕\N{\rYUANWEN}He- - He saw that I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.96,0:40:58.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他在哪\N{\rYUANWEN}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.21,0:41:05.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,被他们带走了\N{\rYUANWEN}They took him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.22,0:41:15.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她们愿意让我们见凯斯勒了\N{\rYUANWEN}They're gonna let us see Kessler.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.06,0:41:19.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那是\N{\rYUANWEN}Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.86,0:41:22.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不是凯斯勒\N{\rYUANWEN}It's not Kessler.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.93,0:41:54.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,致远星不仅是一个地方\N{\rYUANWEN}Reach was more than a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.27,0:41:56.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,更是一个象征\N{\rYUANWEN}It was a symbol.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.93,0:41:59.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是人类精神的丰碑\N{\rYUANWEN}It was a monument to the human spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.77,0:42:05.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,纪念着牺牲了一切保卫这里的人们\N{\rYUANWEN}and to those who sacrificed everything to defend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.40,0:42:10.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比如雅各布·凯斯上将\N{\rYUANWEN}Those like Admiral Jacob Keyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.95,0:42:16.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,以及这位斯巴达战士 瓦纳克·阿马迪\N{\rYUANWEN}And this Spartan, Vannak Amadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.29,0:42:20.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他在致敬星上出生\N{\rYUANWEN}He was born on Tribute.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.96,0:42:23.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我认识他时他才六岁\N{\rYUANWEN}I met him when he was six.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.75,0:42:25.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我能看得出来 他很有荣誉感\N{\rYUANWEN}I could see he had honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.46,0:42:29.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他生活在大家族里\N{\rYUANWEN}He had a large family.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.13,0:42:31.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他尽忠效劳 他的家人会为他骄傲的\N{\rYUANWEN}They would be proud of his service.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.94,0:42:43.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他的家人在他六岁时就埋葬了他\N{\rYUANWEN}His family buried him when he was six.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.77,0:42:46.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们从来不了解他\N{\rYUANWEN}They never knew him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.49,0:42:52.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我了解\N{\rYUANWEN}But I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.50,0:43:05.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他的名字是瓦纳克-134\N{\rYUANWEN}His name was Vannak- 134.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.17,0:43:09.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他是个斯巴达战士\N{\rYUANWEN}He was a Spartan.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.51,0:43:12.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是我们的兄弟\N{\rYUANWEN}He was our brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.14,0:43:14.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他也是自己认识的唯一的亲人\N{\rYUANWEN}And the only family that he ever knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.35,0:43:22.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他 他这一生并不平凡\N{\rYUANWEN}This...This was not an ordinary man.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.31,0:43:28.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他做过的一切 付出的一切\N{\rYUANWEN}Everything that he was, everything that he gave.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.20,0:43:34.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,永垂不朽\N{\rYUANWEN}it never dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.05,0:43:51.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你的战斗没有结束\N{\rYUANWEN}Your fight is not done.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.63,0:43:55.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在我会成为你的武器\N{\rYUANWEN}I will be your weapon now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.51,0:44:00.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会找到害死你的人\N{\rYUANWEN}I will find the ones who caused your death,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.18,0:44:02.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,要了他们的命\N{\rYUANWEN}and I will end them.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.62,0:45:07.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你觉得你能接近巴拉戈斯基\N{\rYUANWEN}You think you can get to Parangosky?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.38,0:45:08.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,接近艾克森吗\N{\rYUANWEN}To Ackerson?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.58,0:45:10.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你连他们在哪里都不知道\N{\rYUANWEN}You don't even know where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.13,0:45:11.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会找到他们的\N{\rYUANWEN}I'll find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.46,0:45:12.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你只会害死你自己\N{\rYUANWEN}You're gonna get yourself killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.30,0:45:17.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我没有选择你\N{\rYUANWEN}I didn't choose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.39,0:45:26.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我找到了你\N{\rYUANWEN}I found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.31,0:45:28.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不管是什么东西打造了光环\N{\rYUANWEN}Whatever built the Halo,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.81,0:45:31.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不管是什么东西留下了那些制品\N{\rYUANWEN}whatever left those artifacts behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.61,0:45:34.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,它们也在你的内心留下了点什么\N{\rYUANWEN}left something in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.44,0:45:35.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你逃避不了的\N{\rYUANWEN}You can't run from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.82,0:45:39.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是你一辈子的召唤\N{\rYUANWEN}This has been calling to you your whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.66,0:45:41.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是你注定要完成的使命\N{\rYUANWEN}This is what you're meant to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.58,0:45:45.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我现在只有一件事情要做 那就是找到巴拉戈斯基和艾克森\N{\rYUANWEN}The only thing I have to do is find Parangosky, Ackerson.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.50,0:45:50.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,约翰 你能带我们去光环\N{\rYUANWEN}John, you can take us to the Halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.92,0:45:55.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们种族能不能活下来 就看光环能教会我们什么了\N{\rYUANWEN}The survival of our species depends on what it can teach us.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.26,0:46:00.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果你自己去找海军情报局报仇 那就是让我们所有人陪你冒险\N{\rYUANWEN}If you go after ONI yourself, you put all of that at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.30,0:46:03.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们不会给你留生路的\N{\rYUANWEN}They can't let you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.31,0:46:10.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我已经死了\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.70,0:46:24.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,加入我们\N{\rYUANWEN}Join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.20,0:46:27.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rYUANWEN}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.71,0:46:32.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不好意思 你\N{\rYUANWEN}Sorry, did
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.38,0:46:36.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你刚才和我说了什么吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Did you say something to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.17,0:46:40.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我代表星球说话\N{\rYUANWEN}I speak for the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.39,0:46:43.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.05,0:46:45.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我代表所有星球说话\N{\rYUANWEN}I speak for all the planets.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.98,0:46:49.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.69,0:46:55.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,人都去\N{\rYUANWEN}Where is.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.90,0:46:57.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我代表牧歌星说话\N{\rYUANWEN}I speak for Madrigal.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.82,0:47:03.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\rYUANWEN}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.32,0:47:05.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我痛苦地呐喊\N{\rYUANWEN}I cry out in painl
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.74,0:47:07.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我的孩子灰飞烟灭\N{\rYUANWEN}My children are ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.75,0:47:09.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我的皮肤破裂 我的心\N{\rYUANWEN}My skin is broken. My heart- -
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.71,0:47:12.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你是谁啊  -你是谁\N{\rYUANWEN}Who the hell are you? - Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.88,0:47:20.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谁也不是\N{\rYUANWEN}No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.55,0:47:23.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你是关哈\N{\rYUANWEN}You're Kwan Ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.76,0:47:25.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哈氏一族最后一人\N{\rYUANWEN}Last of the Has.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.23,0:47:32.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你怎么\N{\rYUANWEN}How do you
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.60,0:47:36.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你是谁  -你背叛了我们\N{\rYUANWEN}Who are you? - You turned your back on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.11,0:47:38.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你忘记了自己的姓名  -别过来\N{\rYUANWEN}You forgot your name. - Get away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.61,0:47:39.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,靠近了\N{\rYUANWEN}It's close now.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.44,0:47:42.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-怪物  -你别过来\N{\rYUANWEN}The monster. Stay where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.61,0:47:44.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,帮助我 找到我\N{\rYUANWEN}Help me. Find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.78,0:47:47.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,拯救我 解救我\N{\rYUANWEN}Deliver me. Save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.58,0:47:49.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不要否认你的使命\N{\rYUANWEN}Do not deny your purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.12,0:47:51.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-不要抛弃你的姓名  -别说了\N{\rYUANWEN}Do not forsake your name. - Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.91,0:47:53.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,守护者\N{\rYUANWEN}Protector.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.09,0:48:00.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\rYUANWEN}What did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.63,0:48:41.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你做了什么 我们怎么在博爱城
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.05,0:48:44.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们的舰队被召回了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.88,0:48:47.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不 我们有任务 要去找回
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.30,0:48:51.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,任务失败了 接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.60,0:48:56.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你知道他们会怎么对我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.27,0:48:57.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,怎么对我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.90,0:49:01.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,只能希望 他们会接受这个信物
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.28,0:49:04.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,作为我失败的补偿
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.16,0:49:08.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.91,0:49:11.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,高等先知已经下令了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.16,0:49:13.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,高等先知是骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.16,0:49:18.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你再辱骂一句 我就撕碎你
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.67,0:49:20.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,先知满嘴谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.09,0:49:23.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们根本没想着开启朝圣之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.34,0:49:26.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们没有能力这么做 他们非天选之人
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.55,0:49:29.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们心知肚明 这是我们的命运 我看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.93,0:49:32.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你能带领我们前往圣迹环带
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.85,0:49:37.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你拍的马屁既残忍又空洞
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.27,0:49:40.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这些先知让你为此感到羞愧 因为他们惧怕你
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.31,0:49:43.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们看到了你的伟大和你纯粹的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.82,0:49:48.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们因自己的虚伪而窒息
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.74,0:50:30.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.16,0:50:35.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不是我 是你
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.54,0:50:39.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是你的命运 你只要接受就好
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.25,0:50:43.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.25,0:50:48.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,相信 你要相信 相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.72,0:50:50.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是世尊者
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.68,0:50:56.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们会派出一整支舰队来追捕我们
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.89,0:50:59.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们会失败的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.02,0:51:03.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一切早已命中注定
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.24,0:52:35.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,需要帮忙吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.66,0:52:38.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有手套吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Gloves?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.74,0:52:41.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就在那边\N{\rYUANWEN}Right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.59,0:52:50.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是你\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.59,0:52:52.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你这样我没认出来\N{\rYUANWEN}I didn't recognize you with your
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.88,0:52:56.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有带刺铁丝网吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Do you have any barbed wire?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.76,0:53:02.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那个和你一起的家伙呢\N{\rYUANWEN}Where's that, uh, fella that was with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.10,0:53:03.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他想来的\N{\rYUANWEN}He wanted to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.77,0:53:07.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我觉得这样不太慎重\N{\rYUANWEN}But I didn't think that would be prudent.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.61,0:53:09.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,慎重\N{\rYUANWEN}Prudent?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.73,0:53:15.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他有点情绪化\N{\rYUANWEN}He can be a bit emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.91,0:53:20.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这种情况我看得更明白\N{\rYUANWEN}Whereas I see this kind of situation a bit more clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.79,0:53:25.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-我没明白  -你肯定明白\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't think I understand. - Of course you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.21,0:53:27.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你以前有过妈妈 对吧\N{\rYUANWEN}You had a mother, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.04,0:53:29.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-对  -没有人应该挡在\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah. - No one should come
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.96,0:53:31.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,妈妈和孩子之间\N{\rYUANWEN}between a mother and her child.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.96,0:53:33.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这个纽带很强大\N{\rYUANWEN}It's a powerful bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.97,0:53:36.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,天生的\N{\rYUANWEN}Instinctive.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.63,0:53:39.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们这里来过很多孩子\N{\rYUANWEN}You know, we got a lot of kids coming through here- -
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.43,0:53:47.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,几天前\N{\rYUANWEN}The other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.48,0:53:50.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我在空气里闻到了一丝气味 让我回到了\N{\rYUANWEN}I caught a scent in the air, that took me back
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.82,0:53:53.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我第一次给凯斯勒剪头发的时候\N{\rYUANWEN}to the first time I cut Kessler's hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.65,0:53:56.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他那时还那么小\N{\rYUANWEN}He was so little.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.11,0:53:59.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,女士 我就是个开店的\N{\rYUANWEN}Look, lady, I- I'm just a businessman.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.28,0:54:00.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他扭来扭去\N{\rYUANWEN}He was squirming.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.12,0:54:04.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我担心会划伤他\N{\rYUANWEN}I was nervous that I would hurt him.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.12,0:54:09.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那个时候我就知道\N{\rYUANWEN}And that's when I knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.83,0:54:12.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果谁伤害了他\N{\rYUANWEN}that if anyone ever caused him pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.34,0:54:14.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我也不知道自己会做出什么\N{\rYUANWEN}there's no telling what I would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.92,0:54:17.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不惜一切\N{\rYUANWEN}There would be no limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.85,0:54:24.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你知道我的意思吧\N{\rYUANWEN}You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.20,0:54:38.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他说了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Did he talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.65,0:54:40.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,说了\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.66,0:54:42.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他说了凯斯勒是被谁带走的吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Did he say who took Kessler?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.49,0:54:45.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,联合国太空指挥部\N{\rYUANWEN}The UNSC.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.34,0:55:03.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,十分钟后出发\N{\rYUANWEN}We're wheels up in ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.02,0:55:07.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,里兹\N{\rYUANWEN}Riz.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.56,0:55:10.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-收拾一下  -我做不到了\N{\rYUANWEN}get your stuff- - - I'm not gonna make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.90,0:55:13.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你说什么呢\N{\rYUANWEN}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.07,0:55:16.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你没事的  -我要留在这里\N{\rYUANWEN}You're gonna be fine. I'm gonna stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.07,0:55:20.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,集中注意力打仗\N{\rYUANWEN}Get your head in the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.74,0:55:23.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我的战争结束了 长官\N{\rYUANWEN}My fight's over, Chief,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.16,0:55:32.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,瓦纳克说结束时才结束\N{\rYUANWEN}It's over when Vannak says it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.25,0:55:34.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-凯说  -士官长\N{\rYUANWEN}When Kai says- - Chief
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.42,0:55:35.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,赢了才算结束\N{\rYUANWEN}It's over when we win!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.42,0:55:39.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,站起来\N{\rYUANWEN}On your feet
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.26,0:55:45.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我命令你 斯巴达战士\N{\rYUANWEN}I gave you an order, Spartan.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.51,0:55:48.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,站起来\N{\rYUANWEN}Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.41,0:56:08.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们失去了致远星\N{\rYUANWEN}We lost Reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.24,0:56:10.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们失去了瓦纳克\N{\rYUANWEN}We lost Vannak
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.41,0:56:11.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-凯  -我知道\N{\rYUANWEN}Kai- I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.75,0:56:14.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那你打算怎么做\N{\rYUANWEN}Then what are you gonna do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.71,0:56:16.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我要活下去\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm going to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.92,0:56:22.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你没资格说不\N{\rYUANWEN}You don't get to say no to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.26,0:56:24.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是我们欠他们的 里兹\N{\rYUANWEN}We owe them, Riz.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.64,0:56:25.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们失去了他们\N{\rYUANWEN}We lost them.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.31,0:56:29.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-我失去了他们  -只是痛苦而已\N{\rYUANWEN}I lost them. It's just pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.77,0:56:32.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你能做的只有带着痛苦前行\N{\rYUANWEN}All you can do is carry it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.98,0:56:35.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,它很沉重\N{\rYUANWEN}But it's heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.11,0:56:38.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但你越不愿面对 越逃避\N{\rYUANWEN}And the more you deny it, the more you run from it,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.98,0:56:40.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,它就会变得越沉重\N{\rYUANWEN}the heavier it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.07,0:56:45.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果你不和痛苦和解 你会被压垮的\N{\rYUANWEN}If you don't make peace with it, it will crush you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.99,0:56:48.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不会让痛苦压垮我\N{\rYUANWEN}I won't let it crush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.58,0:56:55.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我只有你了\N{\rYUANWEN}You're all I have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.13,0:57:00.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rYUANWEN}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.86,0:57:22.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她不来了\N{\rYUANWEN}She's not coming
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.16,0:57:36.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你现在谁也不是了\N{\rYUANWEN}you're no one now.
